But... what if you have a `list` of `list` ? (or a mutable object containing mutable objects)

::: {#68701129 .cell ExecuteTime='{"end_time":"2021-01-15T08:34:50.522523Z","start_time":"2021-01-15T08:34:50.515916Z"}' slideshow='{"slide_type":"fragment"}' execution_count=140}
